Reclusa::

She smiled and moved slowly towards the bench.  "Let me see, the
phasic shields will be helpful in battle. It remodulates it's
frequency after every other hit. However, it also works well on
shuttles as well as missles. Just a thought for our Unicron pain in
the lower base of the spinal structure." she said with a smirk. "But
for myself, I was looking for possible an upgrade to a different style
of body armor. It would take some work, but it can be made to merge
with the phasic shields and the transmetal skin."  she hoped he was
picking up on her hints.
